refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public static staticDatePeriod::createFromISO8601String stringspecification intoptions0
从 ISO8601 字符串创建一个新的 DatePeriod 对象，该字符串由 specification 指定。

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 创建一个新的 DatePeriod 对象。



 通过此方法创建的 DatePeriod 对象可用作迭代器，用于生成多个 DateTimeImmutable 对象。

  &reftitle.examples;



    DatePeriod::createFromISO8601String 示例


<?php
$iso = 'R4/2023-07-01T00:00:00Z/P7D';
$period = DatePeriod::createFromISO8601String($iso);

// By iterating over the DatePeriod object, all of the
// recurring dates within that period are printed.
foreach ($period as $date) {
    echo $date->format('Y-m-d'), "\n";
}


    &example.outputs;


2023-07-01
2023-07-08
2023-07-15
2023-07-22
2023-07-29
